name: Frankie!
description:
All our buddies are unique and completely hand made and just about the quirkiest and cutest gifts or accessories on earth!
And Frankie is no exception :) 

Over 30cms (12inches) long and very colourful with patches such as the union jack (on his adorable little tail), denim and skulls :D

we are sure that reading 'SOLD OUT' won't come as a shock.. look how cute he is! :)

name: Sonny!
description:
All our buddies are unique and completely hand made and just about the quirkiest and cutest gifts or accessories on earth!
And Sonny is no exception :)

He's a little fella - about 7 inches long and has a playful and innocent but  slightly evil air about him; with his open, ready to cuddle arms and slightly disturbing smile.
His head, body, and arms are nice and stipey and he has starrey legs - incredibly cute! :D

name: Mrs Kit 'E' Kat
description:
All our buddies are unique and completely hand made and just about the quirkiest and cutest gifts or accessories on earth!
And Mrs Kit 'E' Kat is no exception :)

Standing at 7-8 inches, she looks unhinged... disturbed... pure evil you might say. Although she is completely adorable, with a touch of the odd housewife about her; and a cute perky tail too.
Her eyes are striking and may just follow you around a room...!
So unique and different and has a slightly goth feel.
A perfect gift for someone with the quirky and maybe slightly disturbed personality! :D

name: Gladys
description:
All our buddies are unique and completely hand made and just about the quirkiest and cutest gifts or accessories on earth!
And Gladys is no exception :)

We think Gladys is one of the most loveable laydeez we've EVER seen here at cookiehooker.
Let's face it, she's no looker, but everyone who sees her falls in love!
Her slightly terrifying face puts you in mind of an old witch, but her cute little ensemble of makeshift dungarees and stripey tshirt is just too adorable to not immediately swoon over.
And her cuteness is amplified even more by those odd limbs, funny features and strands of hair. :)
